  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-ON-02 adversarial)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed. All 13 credibility factors are assessed; achieved levels meet or exceed required levels at the stated operating conditions. Decision: Accepted. NOTE (adversarial): the ContextOfUse description enumerates operating ranges in prose but no hasOperatingEnvelope or hasApplicabilityConstraint link is emitted, leaving the formal model applicability boundary unspecified.",
