      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented test suite covering hemolysis model routines; QA plan traceable to CFD solver release.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2022R2) is under version control with a documented QA plan. Unit and regression tests cover the user-defined hemolysis scalar transport routines. Achieved level equals required level for MRL 5 at this factor."
    },
    {
