      "acceptanceCriteria": "Method of manufactured solutions (MMS) applied to governing equations; order of accuracy confirmed within 10% of theoretical rate.",
      "rationale": "MMS applied to the incompressible Navier-Stokes and scalar hemolysis transport equations. Observed spatial order of accuracy is 1.92 (theoretical 2.0); temporal order 1.97. Code verification requirement met."
