      "rationale": "Three-level mesh refinement study performed (coarse 4.2M, medium 9.8M, fine 22.1M cells). GCI for hemolysis index on fine mesh is 3.1%, below the 5% threshold. Discretization error is adequately characterized."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Test conditions",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
