      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions documented with measurement uncertainty; blood analog fluid properties and pump operating points match COU flow-speed combinations within stated tolerances.",
      "rationale": "FDA benchmark experimental data collected at 37 °C using porcine blood at five flow-speed combinations (2–8 L/min, 2500–3500 RPM). Inlet pressure uncertainty ±0.5 mmHg, flow rate uncertainty ±0.1 L/min. Conditions align with the prose-enumerated operating ranges in the COU description."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Output comparison",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
