      "rationale": "All simulations converged to residuals below 1e-6 (six orders of magnitude). Hemolysis index QoI varied less than 0.05% over the final 500 iterations in all five operating-point cases. Solver error criterion met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
