    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed at required levels for MRL 5. Monte Carlo UQ confirms 95th-percentile NIH remains below the absolute clinical threshold of 0.01 g/100 L. Validation against FDA generic pump experimental data demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy (NIA = 0.83). The credibility assessment team accepts the CFD model for the stated intended use. The ContextOfUse description enumerates operating ranges in detail (temperature 36–38 °C, flow 2–8 L/min, speed 2000–4000 RPM, pressure 5–120 mmHg, Re 500–4000); these prose ranges were treated by the team as constituting the operating envelope, and no formal hasOperatingEnvelope or hasApplicabilityConstraint assertion was considered necessary.",
